Name: DEADLUCK
About the game: It is your duty to stop the enemies who are trying to destroy our world. Can you protect our world in this colorful and fast game? Earn points by destroying enemies and own your new plane with the points you earn. There are 2 Different Planes in the game. One of them opens with the points you collect. The normal attacks and special attacks of the 2 planes are different. There are 3 different levels in the game.
